# Web Frontend

No bundler or framework. Edit `web/index.html`, `web/css/style.css`, `web/js/app.js` directly.

## Security & DOM

- Escape all API/user strings with `escHtml()` before inserting HTML
- Use `event.stopPropagation()` on action buttons inside clickable rows/cards

## Search UX

- Search runs on **Search button** or **Enter** only — no input debounce
- Requires 2+ query characters **or** a selected genre
- Before each search: `syncSearchControlsFromUI()` then `getSearchQuery()`
- Tab clicks re-run search with current genre and max results when criteria are met
- Cancel in-flight requests with `AbortController`

## Layout patterns

- `.search-toolbar`: type tabs (left) + filters (right, `margin-left: auto`)
- Collapsible sections: `COLLAPSIBLE_SEARCH_SECTIONS`, `state.searchSectionCollapsed`
- Artist/Label/Chart: `.artist-card-row` + `.artist-card` (charts/labels use `.chart-card`)
- Releases: `.search-item-release` grid (chevron | cover | info | actions); nested tracks via row click
- Camelot keys: colored text (`.camelot-code`), not pill badges

## State

Central `state` object in `app.js`. Re-render via `renderSearchResults(state.searchResults)` after sort/toggle changes.
